### ========================================
### 2. CREATE PROJECT
### POST /projects
### ========================================

### 2.1 Tạo project thành công (đầy đủ thông tin)
POST {{baseUrl}}/projects
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: {{token}}

{
  "projectName": "Task Manager System",
  "projectDescription": "A system to manage tasks and projects"
}

###

### 2.2 Tạo project tối thiểu (không có description)
POST {{baseUrl}}/projects
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: {{token}}

{
  "projectName": "Minimal Project"
}

###

### 2.3 Thiếu projectName → expect 400
POST {{baseUrl}}/projects
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: {{token}}

{
  "projectDescription": "No name provided"
}

###

### 2.4 projectName rỗng → expect 400
POST {{baseUrl}}/projects
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: {{token}}

{
  "projectName": "",
  "projectDescription": "Blank name"
}

###

### 2.5 projectName vượt 255 ký tự → expect 400
POST {{baseUrl}}/projects
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: {{token}}

{
  "projectName": "AAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAA",
  "projectDescription": "Name too long"
}

###

### 2.6 Không có token → expect 401
POST {{baseUrl}}/projects
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "projectName": "Unauthorized Project"
}


### ========================================
### 3. UPDATE PROJECT
### PATCH /projects/{projectId}
### ========================================

### 3.1 Cập nhật project thành công
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/projects/22
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: {{token}}

{
  "projectName": "Updated Project Name",
  "projectDescription": "Updated description"
}

###

### 3.2 Cập nhật chỉ tên (xóa description)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/projects/22
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: {{token}}

{
  "projectName": "Only Name Updated"
}

###

### 3.3 Project không tồn tại → expect 404
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/projects/99999
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: {{token}}

{
  "projectName": "Ghost Project"
}

###

### 3.4 Thiếu projectName → expect 400
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/projects/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: {{token}}

{
  "projectDescription": "No name"
}

###

### 3.5 Không phải ADMIN của project → expect 403
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/projects/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer <token_of_member_role>

{
  "projectName": "Should be forbidden"
}

###

### 3.6 Không có token → expect 401
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/projects/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "projectName": "Unauthorized update"
}


### ========================================
### 4. UPDATE PROJECT STATUS
### PATCH /projects/{projectId}/status
### ========================================

### 4.1 Chuyển status → ACTIVE
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/projects/1/status
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: {{token}}

{
  "status": "ACTIVE"
}

###

### 4.2 Chuyển status → ON_HOLD
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/projects/1/status
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: {{token}}

{
  "status": "ON_HOLD"
}

###

### 4.3 Chuyển status → COMPLETED
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/projects/1/status
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: {{token}}

{
  "status": "COMPLETED"
}

###

### 4.4 Chuyển status → ARCHIVED
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/projects/1/status
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: {{token}}

{
  "status": "ARCHIVED"
}

###

### 4.5 Status không hợp lệ → expect 400
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/projects/1/status
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: {{token}}

{
  "status": "INVALID_STATUS"
}

###

### 4.6 Thiếu status → expect 400
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/projects/1/status
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: {{token}}

{}

###

### 4.7 Project không tồn tại → expect 404
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/projects/99999/status
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: {{token}}

{
  "status": "ACTIVE"
}

###

### 4.8 Không phải ADMIN của project → expect 403
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/projects/1/status
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer <token_of_member_role>

{
  "status": "ACTIVE"
}


### ========================================
### 5. RESTORE PROJECT
### PATCH /projects/{projectId}/restore
### ========================================

### 5.1 Khôi phục project đã xóa thành công
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/projects/1/restore
Authorization: {{token}}

###

### 5.2 Project chưa bị xóa → expect lỗi (tùy logic)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/projects/2/restore
Authorization: {{token}}

###

### 5.3 Project không tồn tại → expect 404
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/projects/99999/restore
Authorization: {{token}}

###

### 5.4 Không phải người tạo project → expect 403
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/projects/1/restore
Authorization: Bearer <token_of_non_creator>

###

### 5.5 Không có token → expect 401
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/projects/1/restore


### ========================================
### 6. DELETE PROJECT
### DELETE /projects/{projectId}
### ========================================

### 6.1 Xóa project thành công (soft delete)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/projects/1
Authorization: {{token}}

###

### 6.2 Project không tồn tại → expect 404
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/projects/99999
Authorization: {{token}}

###

### 6.3 Không phải ADMIN của project → expect 403
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/projects/1
Authorization: Bearer <token_of_member_role>

###

### 6.4 Không có token → expect 401
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/projects/1
